category: Perl Doc
requires: perl perl-IO-stringy perl-Glib perl-Gtk2 perl-Locale-gettext perl-Pod-Simple
sdesc: "Gtk2 Perl POD viewer module"
ldesc: "podviewer provides a simple and attractive way to read Perl's 
